snippet.title: Magic Mike XXL's Female Stars Dish On the Film's Lap Dances and More
snippet.description:
Jada Pinkett Smith, Amber Heard and co-stars dish on what it was like on set of "Magic Mike XXL" with Wonderwall.com's Kirby Kristen. SUBSCRIBE: http://goo.gl/usQSdP 

About the series: Wonderwall editors sit down with the cast of Hollywood's most popular movies and blockbusters. Tune in as Wonderwall chats with your favorite celebs about their new flicks, celebrity gossip and news before that next big project hits the big screen!
